{"tid":900094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊引《蜘蛛俠》名句「點醒」從政者不應盲從民意","createTime":"2018-11-13T03:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T06:06:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"acc18f45daba42c00d62fcc9f6b77c63f772258c","tid":900094,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181113/large/1542076255_ed78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181113%2Flarge%2F1542076255_ed78.jpg&h=9f9e28f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國漫畫界「教父」、《漫威漫畫》（Marvel）創辦人史丹利（Stan Lee）逝世，享年95歲。Stan創作的多個超級英雄家傳戶曉，身兼行政會議成員的民主思路召集人湯家驊今早亦在Facebook分享Stan逝世的消息，期間更引用《蜘蛛俠》名句，寄語從政者不應盲從民意。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊於Facebook指，Stan筆下的《蜘蛛俠》有一名句：「權力帶來責任；愈大的權力，愈大的責任（With great power comes great responsibility）」，形容「但這是什麼責任卻存在很大爭議性」。他繼而指，一位負責任的從政者「不應盲目追逐民意，而應帶領人民走上光明之路，為整體社會尋求最大的共同福祉」，並以反問「你呢？」作結，未有指明道姓。"},{"pid":"eed811c54f56236ee276f1f217333b07d862f4d0","tid":900094,"uid":53687,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八"},{"pid":"4b7e3397201631253cdfd4b547ea9640f7d8f7c3","tid":900094,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:15:16.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85a67439ca1323df24880c78b7ad6cf56dd47c9","tid":900094,"uid":59536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acc18f45daba42c00d62fcc9f6b77c63f772258c","tid":900094,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181113/large/1542076255_ed78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181113%2Flarge%2F1542076255_ed78.jpg&h=9f9e28f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國漫畫界「教父」、《漫威漫畫》（Marvel）創辦人史丹利（Stan Lee）逝世，享年95歲。Stan創作的多個超級英雄家傳戶曉，身兼行政會議成員的民主思路召集人湯家驊今早亦在Facebook分享Stan逝世的消息，期間更引用《蜘蛛俠》名句，寄語從政者不應盲從民意。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊於Facebook指，Stan筆下的《蜘蛛俠》有一名句：「權力帶來責任；愈大的權力，愈大的責任（With great power comes great responsibility）」，形容「但這是什麼責任卻存在很大爭議性」。他繼而指，一位負責任的從政者「不應盲目追逐民意，而應帶領人民走上光明之路，為整體社會尋求最大的共同福祉」，並以反問「你呢？」作結，未有指明道姓。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"引用下 外國都有神父搞細佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75607d03b62c623bd642e03aa1f81c53eaabff39","tid":900094,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5b78121ff44c4c8a0b1cd568b340fb6a45c71c","tid":900094,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"你幾時死呀 11哥"},{"pid":"b37b1a931ba979063a36cb1215315598d2488069","tid":900094,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"eed811c54f56236ee276f1f217333b07d862f4d0","tid":900094,"uid":53687,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"佢淨係搭十一架咋"},{"pid":"c66e958aab7e8691553e7ade9267911c6bdcccd3","tid":900094,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"講乜鳩呀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解可以拉埋一齊講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad906b1debe740cb25d268edb4f631fa9cf60b6","tid":900094,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"中二病"},{"pid":"64b282d46d7dc888a535c04ed43d2d76630f7a8f","tid":900094,"uid":152476,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/btWwBb75Tfhh6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li